Application: Cascade-Restrict Deadlock Simple
  Description: A cascade B restrict C transitive deadlock must fail at compile time (TERMIN-S codes d)
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000013

Identity:
  Scopes are "dl.view", "dl.manage"
  A "tester" has "dl.view" and "dl.manage"

Content called "as":
  Each a has a label which is text, required
  Anyone with "dl.view" can view as
  Anyone with "dl.manage" can create as

Content called "bs":
  Each b has a label which is text, required
  Each b has an a which references as, required, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "dl.view" can view bs
  Anyone with "dl.manage" can create bs

Content called "cs":
  Each c has a label which is text, required
  Each c has a b which references bs, required, restrict on delete
  Anyone with "dl.view" can view cs
  Anyone with "dl.manage" can create cs
